HEADWORD: Fleckless
<hw>Fleck"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without spot or blame.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My consnience will not count me <qex>fleckless</qex>.</q>
